         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288"><!-- p2l4-r9 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Hd1e108">Rubrica 9</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De litibus et iurgiis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>
      ¶ De litibus et iurgiis. Rubrica. 9.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e115">SAlomon in prouer. c. 13.</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e125">Inter superbos
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>semper iurgia sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e131"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e127">17. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e133">Melior
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>est bucella sicca cum gaudio quam do
        <lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>mus plena victimis cum iurgio. Semper iurgia
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>querit malus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e144"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e142">18. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e146">Os stulti iurgia prouocat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e150">
               <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e152">Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e154">Non litiges
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>cum homine potente: ne forte incidas in manus
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>illius. Non contendas cum viro locuplete: ne <unclear>ec</unclear> <!--contra?-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>consistat litem tibi: multos enim perdidit aurum
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>et argentum vsque <sic>corregum</sic> extendit et conuertit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e166">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e177">28. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e170">Abstine te a lite: et minues peccata.
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>Homo iracundus incendit litem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e176">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e189">Cronica de nugisphilosophurum. c. 5 scilicet de pictago.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e180">Pictagus mitilenus qui fuit vnus de septem
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>sapientibus dicebat: Non obiurgare amicum
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>immo nec inimicum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e190">
               <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e204">Ouidius de arte amandi li. i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e194">Iurgia praecipue vino stimulata caueto.
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>Est nimium facilis ad fera bella manus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e202"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e215">Li. 2</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e204">Esse procul lites: et amare premia lingue.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e211">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e227">Paulus apostolus in epistola. 2. ad timotheum. c. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e215">Seruum deo non oportet litigare: sed mansue
        <lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>tum esse ad omnes: docibilem: patientem: cum mo
        <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>destia corripientem eos qui resistunt veritati.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e225">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e242">Seneca de ira li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e229">Cum pari contendere an
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>ceps est: cum superiore furiosum: cum infe
        <lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>riori sordidum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e237">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e256">Paladius de agricultura. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e241">Uno vel co
        <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>lono confinia possidenti qui fundum aut a
        <lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>grum suum locat: damnis suis ac litibus studet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e249">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e270">Lex diges. ti. de alienatione iudi. etc. l. item
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>si res. in fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e253">Uerecunda cogitatio eius qui li
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>tes execratur: non est vituperanda.</quote><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e279">Lex codi. ti.
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>de iudi. li. properatur dum. in pn.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qde257">Sepe cause pecu
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>niarie mam criminalibus creare noscuntur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e265">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e294">Auctor lib. de for. honeste vite. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e269">Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>in iurgia disceptationesque descendas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e275">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e306">Cato. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e279">Litem inferre caue cum quo ti
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>bi gratia iuncta est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e286">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e319">Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 4. e. 37.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e290">Longa
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>questio litigantium non tam auget patri
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>monia quam euertit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e298"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e331">Lib. 11. e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e300">Si queri<!--117.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="45-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1" break="no"/>tis lucra: vitate potius damnosa litigia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e312">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e349">Isidorus soliloquiorum lib. 2. c. 25.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e316">Nullus
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>existat sermo iurgiorum qui concordiam diui
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>dat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e324"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e361">26 c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e326">Uita lites. Tolle occasionem <sic>lit.</sic></quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-d1e330">
               <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Rd1e372">Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 29</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34288-Qd1e334">Hoc tibi precipio: vites vt placita semper:
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>Si poteris: quoniam prelia sepe mouent.
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>Questio res minuit: odium creat: incitat iram.
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>Pro lucro damnum: ducere sepe solet.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
